# .eos-personal — patterns that should never appear in committed code
# Used by: scripts/check-personal.py, pre-commit hook, CI
# One regex per line. Lines starting with # are comments. Empty lines ignored.
# Add patterns here when you find personal data leaking into code.

# Personal identity
Kevin\s+Bian

# Personal paths
D:\\\\Main Vault
D:/Main Vault
D:\\Main Vault
C:/Users/Kevin
C:\\\\Users\\\\Kevin
C:\\Users\\Kevin

# Personal coordinates
-34\.928
138\.600

# Personal dates (visa/immigration specific)
# Note: bare dates are OK in comments/examples; these match dates with context
date\(2029,\s*7,\s*1\)
date\(2025,\s*11,\s*25\)
